Quality assessment and extraction

Make jpegs for image quality checking then extract good data.

jpegR

Create small jpegs of satellite imagery for analysis.

extractR

Extracts mean values from Landsat imagery based on locations provided by shape files.

Utilities

Handy helper functions for small tasks.

u_dateR

Creates a data frame of paths, folder names and dates.

u_leapR

Renames incorrectly named leap year image date folders.

u_shpsplitR

A tool for splitting ESRI shape files.
